    {
        "id":"nanath_20",
		"message":"Hi there. I am Nanath. No need to introduce yourself, I know who you are, $playername.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Hi Nanath. You are looking scared.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_22"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_22",
		"message":"Well, one of our ex-clients, Dameni, has put an adverse Shadow spell on us.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"So?",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_24"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_24",
		"message":"It makes us noticeable, and thus vulnerable to being caught - paralysing our honest bread and butter work.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Oh. Sounds awful.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_26"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_26",
		"message":"Umar wants me to handle it. He wants me to get it dispelled, so that Thieves' Guild can work again.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Ah, OK then.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_28"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_28",
		"message":"The thing is I don't know much about Shadow or any other so-called powers. My life has been being an honest thief, a score here, a score there - I don't tangle with the supernatural stuff.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_30"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_30",
		"message":"Can't someone help?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I can help. I've had some dealings with the Shadow.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_32"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"troubling_times",
                "value":40
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_32",
		"message":"Really?  Like what?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Sorry, hush-hush stuff around Loneford and Vilegard.\nYou want my help?",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_40"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_40",
		"message":"Of course. First things first, how can we know the nature of the spell?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_42"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_42",
		"message":"Or its name?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Hmm ...",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_44"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_44",
		"message":"Maybe talking to a Shadow Priest may help?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I'll see what I can do.",
				"nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"troubling_times",
                "value":50
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_70",
		"message":"Oh, back again? I hope you bring good news.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Talion, Shadow Priest, has put it on us after all â€“ the Striking Spectacle Shadow Spell.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_72"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"nanath_72",
		"message":"And?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"And ... I think I have to talk to Talion again.",
				"nextPhraseID":"nanath_80",
				"requires":[
					{
						"requireType":"factionScore",
						"requireID":"troubling_times",
						"value":80,
						"negate":true
