    {
        "id":"tt_talion_10",
        "message":"Oh, that lovely spell! The Striking Spectacle Shadow Spell!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_12"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_12",
        "message":"One of my specials! Just had an opportunity to use it again recently. Went awesome!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"... Why would you do that?  People can get hurt?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_20"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_20",
        "message":"Nonsense! How can being more noticeable hurt? It's makes one stand out more, makes one more popular.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Not if you want to be a spy or similar.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_30"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_30",
        "message":"Why would these so-called spies approach you?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I'm a kid. No one notices me ...",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_40"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_40",
        "message":"That's debatable in your case, but I see the point.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Thanks! So, why did you do it?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_50"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_50",
        "message":"For coins, of course! Why else?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Well, what will it take to remove the spell?",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_60"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"tt_talion_60",
        "message":"Around 50,000 coins, of which a large portion will go back to the mysterious Lady Dameni, who had me do the spell. I would need to pacify her, else her toughs will kill me.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"50,000 coins! Hope the spies can reimburse me.",
                "nextPhraseID":"tt_talion_62"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"troubling_times",
                "value":70
            }
        ]
    },
